            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audius</ex></expan> P</supplied>aternus Cleme<supplied reason="lost">ntianus</supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>urator</ex></expan> Au<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">provinciarum Iudaeae</supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">Sardiniae Africae et Norici</supplied> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>uitum</ex></expan> alae Silia<supplied reason="lost">nae</supplied> <lb n="6"/>torquatae <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ivium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>omanorum</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unus</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">militum</supplied> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">XI <expan><abbr>Claud</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>coh</abbr><ex>ortis</ex></expan> I Cla</supplied>ssica<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied> <lb n="10"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> fecit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In sekundärer Verwendung in einer spätrömischen Mauer gefunden. Sechs teilweise aneinanderpassende Blöcke. Die Maßangabe bezieht sich auf das rekonstruierte Monument (nach lupa 6431). Hedera in Z. 2. (B): IBR 85: allgemein: Abweichungen im Zeilenfall; IBR; Fitz; Lőrincz; Kraft: Z. 3-4 fehlen; IDRE: fehlender Zeilenfall Z. 7/8.</p>
            </div>
